data.label: Toro - Heavy weight, heavy grain, low stretch, high durability The ultimate “biker jacket” leather - durable and heavy enough for any situation life may throw your way. Kobe will take some wearing in, but once it mounds to your body you will never want to wear anything else. PRICE:

Texas - Light weight, heavy grain, medium stretch, high durability.  Everything we love about Kobe, but just a little lighter for those who want a jacket for all seasons and are looking for that ‘worn in’ feel the moment they slip it on.  PRICE:

Nirvana - Medium weight, high stretch, medium durability. Buttery soft lamb skin makes for the most comfortable leather you’ve ever worn, but isn’t for the reckless as it will show slight wear over time (but we think that’s part of what makes a leather jacket so special!) PRICE:

Croc - Heavy weight, heavy grain (textured print), low stretch, high durability. Our signature look, an elevated black option for the customer who loves a black leather but is looking for something *extra* PRICE:
Washed Nero - Medium weight, medium grain, medium stretch, high durability. This veg-tanned leather is the best of both worlds with the feel of lambskin and the durability of cowskin.

Shark - Medium weight, heavy grain, high stretch, medium durability. Irresistibly soft and stretchy for such a heavy and grained leather, this is going to break into the ultimate “vintage” looking jacket. PRICE:

Patent Black - Light weight, low grain, high stretch, high durability Patent leather has a reputation for feeling a bit like plastic… but not this one! With enough stretch to allow you to show off your jacket on any dance floor! PRICE:
Heavy Metal - Medium weight, medium grain, low stretch, high durability  Faded black with just a hint of metallic gives the PERFECT sophisticated rock n’ roll look! PRICE:

Snake - Heavy weight, low stretch, low grain (printed pattern), medium durability Go ALL out with our shimmery snake printed leather. We guarantee no one else will be wearing the same outfit as you in this bad baby! PRICE:

Snake Midnight - Heavy weight, low stretch, low grain (printed pattern), medium durability Go ALL out with our shimmery snake printed leather. We guarantee no one else will be wearing the same outfit as you in this bad baby! PRICE:
Ink Navigator - Heavy weight, heavy grain, low stretch, high durability.  A timeless leather in an inky blue for those who want a classic alternative to black!
Navy - Heavy weight, heavy grain, low stretch, high durability Everything we love about our classic Roma leather in a rich navy blue. PRICE:
Olive - Heavy weight, heavy grain, low stretch, high durability Everything we love about our classic Roma leather in a deep olive green. PRICE:

Crackle - Medium weight, high grain, low stretch, high durability  Metallic + leather = perfection! what could be better for a statement piece! PRICE:
Gold - Heavy weight, low grain, low stretch, high durability  Metallic + leather = perfection! what could be better for a statement piece! PRICE:
Tobacco - Heavy weight, heavy grain, low stretch, high durability Everything we love about our classic Roma leather in a classic tobacco brown. PRICE:
Garnett - Light weight, heavy grain, low stretch, medium durability like a fine wine, this leather will get better with time! PRICE:

Snow - Heavy weight, heavy grain, low stretch, medium durability This leather is durable and heavy enough for any situation life may throw your way, but white is not for the faint of heart! We’ve done our best to source the most resilient white leather we can find, but white is white, so be prepared that your jacket will show wear! PRICE:
